headline: Starbucks to Host 2026 Investor Day on January 29, 2026
summary: SEATTLE, January 22, 2026--Starbucks Coffee Company (NASDAQ: SBUX), today announced plans to unveil its long-term growth strategy at its 2026 Investor Day on Thursday, January 29, 2026. The event will feature presentations, as well as a question-and-answer session with members of the company’s executive leadership team, including Brian Niccol, chairman and chief executive officer, and Cathy Smith, chief financial officer.

headline: Starbucks price target raised to $114 from $106 at BofA
